openapi: "3.1.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example spec with valid links
paths:
  /with-links:
    get:
      operationId: withLinks
      responses:
        '200':
          description: This has links
          content:
            applicaton/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  test:
                    type: string
                    description: A test response fields
                    example: foobar
          links:
            exampleWithOperationId:
              operationId: withLinksTwo
              parameters:
                param: baz
  /with-links-two/{param}:
    parameters:
      - name: param
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      operationId: withLinksTwo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: This has links too
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  test2:
                    type: string
                    description: Another test response
                    example: foobaz
          links:
            exampleWithRef:
              $ref: '#/components/links/exampleWithOperationRef'
components:
  links:
    exampleWithOperationRef:
      operationRef: '/with-links'
